title: Episode 177 - When To Exit The Game (ft. St. Robert Daygame)
description:
Show Notes: 

In this episode, I explore the topic of when to get out of the game with fellow dating coach and world traveler, St. Robert Daygame. We discuss:

How to tell if you're ready for a relationship and which sort of relationship style to choose...
The dangers of staying in the game too long...
The number thing you should do before exiting the game...
How much sex does a guy really need before he feels validated and possible to be monogamous...
What the guys who are masters with women all experience...
